{"tid":1616884,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 究竟學生點樣先可以有效咁係和理非層面做到野","createTime":"2019-10-03T14:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T02:11:41.000Z","uid":239492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"362c68c885f7d0839a6bbd872d4315f987481761","tid":1616884,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"琴日係DI到搞咗次罷課，雖然係叫做多人過上兩次，但係我覺得硬係覺得無咩成效。<br />\n<br />\n所以我想集思廣益一下，特別係暴大，我好想知點解暴大好似可以做得好成功，撇除人地係三大呢類理由。<br />\n<br />\n有人提議過試下做各種嘅聲援活動，例如連儂牆、busking、貼文宣等各種活動，但係我最怕就係件事會變嘉年華<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫幫忙"},{"pid":"795edc4f5dbc168519c5a4b6caf2d5dd662806aa","tid":1616884,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:40:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8342bd30ae8aa167e5fe2373c88f6ab330051aa","tid":1616884,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9796cb255861750dee7e440ba20f276954e85c77","tid":1616884,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:40:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d64231aff0cfa429d985df3ba47ba787b21bba0a","tid":1616884,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:41:18.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n今日開始再無&ldquo;和理非&rdquo;同&ldquo;勇武&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1616733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1616733</a>"},{"pid":"6262662484e1df4e7471e43329a8c0891140e6c6","tid":1616884,"uid":14296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"[多圖多字]你想嘗試挽救身邊既藍屍朋友/家人 可以試下咁做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1616797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1616797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"94cbf376bc426f5b3b7208d0dc48426163bab885","tid":1616884,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da92eae1374a0e626602daf821f084825b8f4d6b","tid":1616884,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike"